data.description: Centrally located home in active Sun City with 8 Recreation Centers to enjoy hundreds of activities, Freshly painted exterior, 2 bed/1.75 bath (Comfy and relaxing Universal walk-in jacuzzi tub in one bath and walk in shower in the other), updated kitchen with newer cabinets, large, tile floor in all the right places, large lot, lots of parking in driveway, easy to enclose carport if you must have a garage, back room for office or storage space and additional storage that can be converted back to golf cart garage. Looking for low electric bills? LARGE 11kw System that generates an estimated yearly production of 18,915 KWH, system is financed (seller will be paying off 50% of the financed amount at close of escrow and has an assumable APR of 1.99% per Mosaic finance company), Willing to HELP with Interest Rate BUYDOWN if needed.
